---
description: Prisma and database rules
globs: ["prisma/**", "**/*.prisma", "lib/db/**", "src/lib/db/**"]
alwaysApply: true
---

Database rules:
- Prefer normalized schema unless denormalization clearly improves performance.
- Always consider indexes for lookup fields.
- Use descriptive relation names.
- When modifying schema, explain impact on existing data.
- Suggest migration command when schema changes.
- Avoid destructive changes unless explicitly requested.